Class Brachiosaur

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Actor
game.dinosaurs.Dinosaur
game.dinosaurs.Brachiosaur
All Implemented Interfaces:
Capable, Printable, ActorInterface, Visitable
public class Brachiosaur
extends Dinosaur
A herbivorous Dinosaur. It can trample Bushes when it steps on it. It can only eat Fruits in Trees.
